{"tid":544095,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(估地方)醫生誤插食道球入氣管充氣漢危殆","createTime":"2018-01-29T07:40:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-30T10:29:25.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"52424482bee5ec4453d3f4fa6497e1e3ca256cd0","tid":544095,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T07:40:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520611/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%A4%E6%8F%92%E9%A3%9F%E9%81%93%E7%90%83%E5%85%A5%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1%E5%85%85%E6%B0%A3%E6%BC%A2%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520611%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%258F%2592%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%2585%2585%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25AE%2586%20&d=DJiSBtXiFTBcJPIruzqCx75jdjnviJyhTm2mNdHk1vQ%3D&h=09844fef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F520611%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E6%258F%2592%25E9%25A3%259F%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%2585%25A5%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E7%25AE%25A1%25E5%2585%2585%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E5%258D%25B1%25E6%25AE%2586%20&h=b89ee691\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/520611/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%A4%E6%8F%92%E9%A3%9F%E9%81%93%E7%90%83%E5%85%A5%E6%B0%A3%E7%AE%A1%E5%85%85%E6%B0%A3%E6%BC%A2%E5%8D%B1%E6%AE%86 </a><br />\n<br />\n威爾斯親王醫院一名六十四歲男病人由於胃出血，醫生幫他置入食道球止血時，懷疑誤將食道球插錯入氣管並充氣，個多小時後另一醫生發現病人氣管穿洞，感染肺炎，現時情況危殆。威院指非常重視事件，已邀請明愛及屯門醫院醫生就臨床處理過程是否恰當，及合符專業水準做核查，同時亦將個案通報醫管局。 <br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名男病人六十四歲，本身患有肝硬化，併發胃及食道靜脈曲張，正在輪候換肝。他本月十日到威院覆診，照胃鏡時醫生發現他的胃靜脈曲張，之後大量出血，醫生即時為其處方血管收縮藥，又注射止嘔藥及鎮靜劑，但未能止血。 <br />\n<br />\n醫院腸胃科外科醫生其後為病人經鼻腔置入食道球緊急止血，確認位置後，將他送入深切治療部。一個多小時後，深切治療部醫生發現不能夠調整到插喉導管位置，用支氣管鏡檢查，發現食道球在氣管內，醫生即時抽出食道球及導管。 <br />\n<br />\n檢查後發現蔡生的氣管有十厘米傷口出血，其中三至四厘米穿洞，他接受手術後有發燒及肺炎，現時用人工肺協助呼吸，目前仍然在威院留醫，情況危殆。 <br />\n<br />\n威院發言人回應指，個案屬罕見手術風險，已經與病人家屬會面解釋過程，醫院非常重視事件，已經邀請明愛同屯門外科顧問醫生就臨床處理過程是否恰當，及合符專業水準作稽核，提供獨立專家意見，稍後再向病人家屬交代結果，同時亦已經將個案通報醫管局。"},{"pid":"04eb3b88263d7e6a218e05a2b67e25feae66c802","tid":544095,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:08:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ff30c00545df01f199d6c5f615678c1f6667b9","tid":544095,"uid":7278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:31:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcd1e93f73b604cee541d5f59cb59555b418c4c","tid":544095,"uid":35014,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:32:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5f7eb1be4ea9800b4fe14b5f53006cfaed7fda89","tid":544095,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:53:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"240f66711a380afa6ead81b38332fbef360ae111","tid":544095,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:55:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b08b22a860aebdafd42b98babde9dc2d794a55f","tid":544095,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T08:57:25.000Z","msg":"果一個鐘咪敢流血, 咪病到仆街?"},{"pid":"1920067bf09fb98aef01f1c0b89846013363b407","tid":544095,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31b9c3a0c14209512062b6c3c0fe96153cd935b1","tid":544095,"uid":55488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2b5